Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.55,0:00:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不赶紧的话  就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的关心  不过今天是周日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在已经是早上10点左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有课  现在也已经迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:29.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  no  看我都做了什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  回去再睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉最近满大小姐傻事越做越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该说她们是变得开朗了  还是不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这果然是因为那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:40.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐也很黏着他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳也很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从风见先生来到这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家变得开朗起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这明明是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却无法坦率地高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是也改变一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改变这种事能被允许吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看电视吧  电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在浴缸里连100都无法数到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有忍耐力的孩子越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以说是「宽松教育」的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又不是我喜欢才对自己宽松的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要成为在浴缸里能数到1万的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能忍的女人事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2404
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2405
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2406
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2407
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2410
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸  饭菜要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道小幸的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去准备些新的冰块才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.49,0:04:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我房间的冰箱里有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜  来帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我能叫您小雄吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸  抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了  真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快考试了他不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我拿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要好好复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的内容会在考试里出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这个世界上会有考试这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试啊  考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话  让考试消失也办的到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别说这种荒谬的事让小幸困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是真的想她那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.87,0:07:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后她就一直把自己关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也一直是电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满说傻话已经是司空见惯的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照往常的话  幸也应该理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管的话  我想也不会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.72,0:08:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之前发生过浴室那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我之后找幸谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给风见君办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前有没有听说过仅仅想让考试消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女生便在学校里放了火这个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚  发生过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事  我就不问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一件事希望你能明确地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会让小岭同学做出什么危险的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生那样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会全力安排好  让幸和你们免受危害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你之前的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  到时希望你能助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须成为好孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得告诉小岭同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没法阻止考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果阿幸还是没来上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天好像很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:11:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以放心了  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被雄二叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被风见先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想偷跑也是白费力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您误会了  我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  叫我们过来的哥哥自己却不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要不先离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是雄二还没过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…都这么晚了  不太安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求各位了  快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身子还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午都请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有事瞒着我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟平时没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太奇怪了  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是快回宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  你们快给我到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  各位也快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来所有人都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在暑假前  整顿一下宿舍的纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管是突然召集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位依然全部到场让我感到很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事在宿舍做不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  所有人都回宿舍去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我收拾一下再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是太莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给风见我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  到底是搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之后肯定会有少儿不宜的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸药…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经改造成倒计为0就停止运行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以外行的水准来说这炸弹相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像吓唬得有点过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了那个城市的  那个公园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了啊  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您终于想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到周围打听了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸运碰到了你的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听他说你的父母遭遇了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家经营着一个小工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然生活艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父母都非常疼爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可一旦工作繁忙起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就没空陪着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟风见先生相遇正好就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从您那寂寞的表情中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了跟自己相似的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您在一起玩耍的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我忘记了寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  您渐渐地不再去那个公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那一天  10岁的生日到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  今天是你的生日  我们就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些日子以来让你那么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定今天一整天都陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想庆祝生日你们两个自己庆祝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是在乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.43,0:16:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原谅他们俩用寂寞两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就概括了我忍受了那么久的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一个人在公园冷静下来后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才发觉到自己说的话是那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.58,0:16:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈成了植物人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的任性  才让他们遭遇事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必须做个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能乖乖听话的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  我在那个城市也想起了一些自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.76,0:17:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你有听到我叫你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时有一点家庭烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情很低落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过多亏了你任性地带我疯玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我心情好了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性有时也能救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的师父也说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她说一句任性话都不懂说  太老实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让人看着就觉得心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母肯定也在你一直忍受着的痛苦里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.08,0:18:06.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想着孩子和工作究竟哪个重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终他们得出了还是要把孩子放在第一的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你父母所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的任性有时也会让父母感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你再多任性一点也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人努力到现在真是辛苦你了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师父还说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不报才可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:19:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那时的我被幸所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那这次当是给她报恩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在把你制作的炸药引爆销毁证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被其他人发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经准备好了对策  把耳朵捂住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是为掩盖爆炸声而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看看烟花也挺不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那次事故之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.25,0:19:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一次都没去探望过看你母亲对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为母亲肯定憎恨着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.91,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可那天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这钥匙是你叔叔给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你10岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你的未来是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你可以永远保持笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是将你的名字起为幸的我们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱对你来说可能还有点难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用这句话表达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你生为我们的孩子  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这话该我说才对  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说虽然不明显
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实有着恢复的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想以后多去探望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.68,0:21:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.59,0:21:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以任性一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.64,0:21:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能请您拥抱我一分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一分钟就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只要这点就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.92,0:23:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  世界树的种子I
